ptolemy.actor.util

Class TimedEvent

  • java.lang.Object
    • ptolemy.actor.util.TimedEvent
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.lang.Comparable<TimedEvent>

    public class TimedEvent
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Comparable<TimedEvent>
    This class aggregates an instance of Time and an Object, and provides a CQComparator as an inner class.
    Since:
    Ptolemy II 0.4
    Author:
    Edward A. Lee and Haiyang Zheng
    See Also:
    CQComparator, Time
